                    username/password: See next paragraph for more info.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
                <h4>Discuss</h4>
                <p>This is the information for the next page. <br> The username is: <b>ticimalko@ymail.com</b> <br> The
                    password is: <b>Hello2022!</b></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-4">
